    "description": "AMIYA Corporation develops, manufactures, and sells cybersecurity products and services. The company designs and operates information security and network infrastructure products; develops and sells security and Saas cloud network products; and detects, assesses, and operates cyber security products. It also operates information system services. In addition, the company offers ALog ConVerter, a server access log management system; ALog ConVerter DB, a database log management system; ALog EVA, an integrated data management tool; and Resource Athlete, a server management system. Further, it provides Verona, a cloud VPN service that offers private company lines over the internet; Hypersonix, a network cloud service that provides business wireless LAN design and operations. The company serves in Japan, Taiwan, China, Hong Kong, Thailand, Vietnam, Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia, the United States, and the United Kingdom. AMIYA Corporation was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
